HORSERADISH CREAM SAUCE

Ingredients
-----------
1 Cup Sour Cream, smallest container
1/4 Cup Horseradish, prepared
1 Tblsp Dijon Mustard
1 Tblsp Mayonnaise
1 tsp Champagne Vinegar
1 tsp Worcestershire Sauce
1/2 bunch Chives, chopped

Mehtod
------
0. Chop the chives.
1. Dump the Sour Cream into the serving dish, medium glass bowl.
2. Add the other ingredients, and mix well.
3. Refrigerate overnight.
4. Place on table when guests arrive.
